      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;text-decoration: underline;&#34;&gt;Trendwatching.com has released its list of &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.trendwatching.com/briefing/&#34;&gt;10 Crucial Consumer Trends of 2010&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.trendwatching.com/briefing/#realtime&#34;&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;size-medium wp-image-621  aligncenter&#34; title=&#34;trends1&#34; src=&#34;https://loudervoice.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/27/2010-the-year-of-real-time-reviews/trends1-300x111.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;trends1&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; height=&#34;111&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/27/2010-the-year-of-real-time-reviews/trends1-300x111.jpg 300w, http://localhost:1313/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/27/2010-the-year-of-real-time-reviews/trends1.jpg 573w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;text-decoration: underline;&#34;&gt;At Number 3 is Real-Time Reviews&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.trendwatching.com/briefing/#realtime&#34;&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;aligncenter size-medium wp-image-622&#34; title=&#34;trends2&#34; src=&#34;https://loudervoice.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/27/2010-the-year-of-real-time-reviews/trends2-300x153.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;trends2&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; height=&#34;153&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/27/2010-the-year-of-real-time-reviews/trends2-300x153.jpg 300w, http://localhost:1313/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/27/2010-the-year-of-real-time-reviews/trends2.jpg 576w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;text-decoration: underline;&#34;&gt;Sometimes we’re just a &lt;em&gt;tiny&lt;/em&gt; bit ahead of the trends here in LouderVoice HQ:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://business.loudervoice.com/2007/06/13/loudervoice-twitter-mash-up/&#34;&gt;&lt;img class=&#34;aligncenter size-full wp-image-623&#34; title=&#34;trends3&#34; src=&#34;https://loudervoice.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/27/2010-the-year-of-real-time-reviews/trends3.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;trends3&#34; width=&#34;598&#34; height=&#34;169&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/27/2010-the-year-of-real-time-reviews/trends3.jpg 598w, http://localhost:1313/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/27/2010-the-year-of-real-time-reviews/trends3-300x84.jpg 300w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;text-decoration: underline;&#34;&gt;That’s why &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/review&#34;&gt;@review&lt;/a&gt; is LouderVoice!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
